    "excerpt": "What classical Ayurveda texts say about exercise — intensity, timing, benefits, and contraindications from the Charaka Samhita.",
    "metaDescription": "Learn Vyayama, Ayurveda's classical exercise framework from Charaka Sutra Sthana — intensity, timing, benefits, and who should avoid it.",
